---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Probst Excavating | Family-Owned Since 2004 | Aurora, IN"
  description="Learn about Probst Excavating - a family-owned excavation company serving Aurora, IN and the Tri-State area for over 20 years with licensed, bonded, and insured services."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
      About Probst Excavating Services
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          At Probst Excavating Services, we've been shaping the future of Aurora, Lawrenceburg, 
          and the Tri-State area for over 20 years. As a family-owned and operated business, 
          we're dedicated to delivering top-quality excavation and site development services 
          tailored to your needs.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          What sets us apart is our hands-on approach. The owner is always on the job site, 
          making sure every project is done right. We believe in personal accountability and 
          building lasting relationships with our customers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">20+ Years of Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Our deep knowledge of Dearborn County's unique terrain ensures we can handle 
              any challenge your property presents.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Family-Owned & Operated</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              When you work with us, you're working directly with the owner who takes 
              personal pride in every project.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Licensed, Bonded & Insured</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We're fully licensed, bonded, and insured, giving you peace of mind that 
              your property is protected.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">State-of-the-Art Equipment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Our modern equipment ensures precision, efficiency, and safety on every job site.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          At Probst Excavating, we bring local expertise, advanced equipment, and a commitment 
          to safety to every job. Whether we're clearing land, excavating foundations, installing 
          utilities, or grading sites, our skilled team ensures precision and efficiency while 
          adhering to strict safety standards.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We prioritize protecting your property and delivering results that stand the test of time. 
          From free estimates to tailored project plans, our customer-first approach means we listen 
          to your needs and deliver results that exceed expectations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>Residential & Commercial Excavation</li>
          <li>Land Clearing for New Construction</li>
          <li>Sewer Line Repair & Replacement (Trenchless Technology)</li>
          <li>Water Line Installation & Repair</li>
          <li>Storm Drainage Systems</li>
          <li>Site Preparation & Grading</li>
          <li>Hydroseeding</li>
          <li>Trucking & Hauling</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">
          Contact us today for a free estimate on your excavation project in Aurora, 
          Lawrenceburg, or anywhere in the Tri-State area.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/contact" 
          class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          Get a Free Estimate
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white mt-16 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Probst Excavating Services. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
        Aurora, IN | Family-Owned & Operated Since 2004
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
